Package Management.Quarter

Class Quarter

java.lang.Object
Management.Quarter.Quarter
Direct Known Subclasses:
DataFundry, InternetFiberProvider, ProductionQuarter
public abstract class Quarter extends Object
This abstract class implements the basic properties and methods of every quarter.

    • loadConstructionInfoPaneValue

      protected void loadConstructionInfoPaneValue()
      Load the information pane for the construction of the quarter. It indicated notably the name, the different construction costs and the maximum level, the maximum number of crew member, the consumptions and the production values once built. The pane also presents the button to build the quarter, which once selected change the value of selectedQuarter in the GlobalManager to the TrueName of the quarter.

    • loadQuarterInfoPane

      public void loadQuarterInfoPane()
      Load the information pane for the construction of the quarter. It indicated notably the name, the level and maximum level, the different consumptions, the number of crew member and its maximum, the production values. The pane also presents the button to upgrade the quarter.
